<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255460>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 11. Dolichomitus excavatus Zwakhals, (8) Scutellum and propodeum, (9) Mid coxa, (10) First to third tergites in dorsal view, (11) Wings. Scale bars (11): 1 mm, (8,10): 0.5 mm, (9): 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255460/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255461>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 20. Dolichomitus koreanus Lee & Choi sp. nov., (12) Habitus in dorsal view, (13) Head in frontal view, (14) Head in lateral view, (15) Head and mesoscutum in dorsal view, (16) Mesosoma in lateral view, (17) Tarsal claw, (18) Wings, (19) Scutellum and propodeum, (20) First to third tergites in dorsal view. Scale bars (12,18): 2 mm, (13 – 16, 19,20): 0.5 mm, (17): 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255461/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.255462>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 29. Dolichomitus rufinus Lee & Choi sp. nov., (21) Habitus in lateral view, (22) Head in frontal view, (23) Head in lateral view, (24) Tarsal claw, (25) Mesosoma in lateral view, (26) Mesoscutum in dorsal view, (27) Scutellum and propodeum, (28) Fore wing, (29) First to third tergites in dorsal view. Scale bars (21,28): 2 mm, (25,29): 1 mm, (22,23,26,27): 0.5 mm, (24): 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/255462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

